    <entry>
      <title>node.js-setup wizard ended prematurely失败解决方法</title>
      <link href="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一步：点击链接下载nodejs安装包<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a></p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/c6d2d6d3a14f438d8e29b6ce72e49f6c.png" class="" title="img"><p>第二步：解压到到一个你通常习惯的盘中比喻c盘 解压可命名为nodejs</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/c3c113296b4243b2ae2686c9dc2c6bc9.png" class="" title="img"><p>修改名称为nodejs</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/0b215bbf9b864547b1edaab5aeb95d0f.png" class="" title="img"><p>第三步：配置环境变量 找到原有的path</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/bd80ebca91924a5eb00a1d6f0f8bd12b.png" class="" title="img"><p>添加nodejs文件路径</p><p>比喻我的路径为</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/99f57d63fc8246199a04af5384d7d60a.png" class="" title="img"><p>配置</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/f585ba6885e3402d9b6ce95a1b83a23f.png" class="" title="img"><p>在配置nodejs文件加下面的node_modules文件夹路径 一定要注意“;”隔开</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/2f8fe6f5a9594873a78c41a0603eb2ec.png" class="" title="img"><p>第四步：安装express</p><p>按wind+r 输入cmd按确定</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/6ad028d932804d8db59b50eead7ba73c.png" class="" title="img"><p>出现</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/3ebf1722f61943128de53a0947ceff81.png" class="" title="img"><p>然后进入node_modules目录</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/e2bede80300949d68d00c417ef38b9ba.png" class="" title="img"><p>在输入命令 npm install express</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/e0f116cd87664a69b8f2b926aabe0ab8.png" class="" title="img"><p>然后会出现以下图片</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/a6f00375ca5e46aa81b64a3fb21148e3.png" class="" title="img"><p>在输入node -v 检查安装版本</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/2f47a7243be54aa4984495f04af55439.png" class="" title="img"><p>在输入npm -v 若出现以下错误 若没出现错误那么久恭喜你安装成功了！</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/d4811e93827d44e8b5038b29e8d01f75.png" class="" title="img"><p>下载可能是npm出问题了需要重新安装npm 地址为： <a href="http://nodejs.org/dist/npm/">http://nodejs.org/dist/npm/</a> 下载后解压 解压后找到npm文件夹然后复制</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/d9aa4464c5e14b04ad7889ba69f0e209.png" class="" title="img"><p>在找到nodejs安装目录下的node_modules文件然后粘贴npm文件夹</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/ebbb0215198d4a08b4b24cd8a7408724.png" class="" title="img"><p>这是在输入 npm -v呈现以下图片那么恭喜你安装成功了！</p><img src= "/pn/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/pn/2020/12/25/%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/370ff60f59064c75aa1bb429ceec4432.png" class="" title="img">]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
